1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with scene analysis and object pose estimation using vision-based techniques. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also a likely category as the paper discusses the application of the proposed method in robotic systems. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper mentions the use of self-supervised learning for feature extraction. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with intelligent systems that require precise scene analysis capabilities. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper discusses the concept of vision as inverse graphics and the use of an inverse rendering module.
